{"tid":1001352,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【#10 Year Challenge】謝偉俊曬恩愛 帶74歲白姐姐去藍田食團年飯","createTime":"2019-01-30T05:39:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-31T09:27:43.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"8eb5981f1ef5d5423c29627335d06be76ddde60e","tid":1001352,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T05:39:15.000Z","msg":"人生有幾多個十年？白姐姐同謝偉俊相差14年，兩人於97年結婚，到今年已經做咗22年夫妻，兩個十年，夫婦倆經歷咗好多嘢。74歲的白姐姐，近年出現公眾場合，除不會再投訴另一半不懂溫柔，更緊隨阿Paul身後表現得小鳥依人。向來喜歡貴婦打扮的白姐姐，大部份時間更以素顏示人反璞歸真。 <br />\n數日前，阿Paul帶着白姐姐去藍田參加活動聚會，與一班政界朋友食團年飯，戴住冷帽的白姐姐，未有悉心打扮，反而換了眼鏡的阿Paul，打扮後生。在酒樓內，阿Paul介紹朋友給白姐姐，寒暄一輪，白姐姐跟阿Paul坐低食飯。<br />\n白姐姐曾經講過阿Paul最愛鋤強扶弱，尤其是最愛鋤她這種強人，現在變得小鳥依人的白姐姐，應該跟阿Paul沒有衝突了。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bfyy5TgljYc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dbfyy5TgljYc&d=CddLi1wVc%2F0RDzQLDYdfB4GitI067obQ02bu1xQE4oc%3D&h=a8c4eddb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bfyy5TgljYc</a>"},{"pid":"ba4bf79b375b83ff50aab2572623248086ce4eef","tid":1001352,"uid":171788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T05:43:55.000Z","msg":"究竟係愛定責任..."},{"pid":"977e8c9ba441301b5142054f6eb4678d8d81a180","tid":1001352,"uid":3232,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T05:52:33.000Z","msg":"尤其是最愛鋤她這種強人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14edd2e30ae3f9c561c36ee7ca1741509bc90ad8","tid":1001352,"uid":186035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T05:53:08.000Z","msg":"阿Paul最愛鋤強扶弱，尤其是最愛鋤她這種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6d0fd91409cce8135b42c32f919add698ccc6ee","tid":1001352,"uid":46587,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score"